  <brief_title>Ascending Aortic Dilation in BiAV After TAVR</brief_title>
  <official_title>Changes in Ascending Aorta Size After Transcatheter Aortic Valve Replacement in Severe Bicuspid Aortic Stenosis: A Pilot Study With Echocardiographic Follow-up</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Seoul National University Hospital</agency>
